        <li>Bird, S. A., Flynn, C., Sekhri, R., et al. (2026). "Galactic Stellar Halo Luminosity Function." <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.11354">arXiv:2603.11354</a>.</li>
        <li>Gaia Collaboration et al. (2021). "Gaia Catalogue of Nearby Stars" — disk LF comparison reference (in text).</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

